title: Cafe Josefina
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, International, Organic, Western, Beer/Wine, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Cafe and bistro operating since Jan 2014. Offers a daily menu with 3 lunches being vegetarian of which 2 are usually vegan. Has smoothies, fresh lemonade, coffee drinks, and usually one of the cakes is vegan. Prices inexpensive-moderate.
